window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The system came. The apocalypse ended. Now new worlds have merged with Earth.</b></p> <p>For Bain Lee, it means leveling his Ocularist class beyond its previous limits. With this strange class and the ability to see into the inner workings of the system, he may find the magic skills needed to earn his redemption. Not only that, but he might discover the secret behind the system itself.</p>"; 
